    "Our data collection pipeline is comprehensive, diverse, and appropriately tailored for children's language models, while also being scalable to support the accumulation of more sources for future development.",
    "Given the size of our collected pre-training data and available resources, we opted to train a masked language model (MLM) to validate the corpus quality and ensure support for the kid-specific properties discussed above.",
